@node LIMIT "PARpro Help: Limitations"



        So, we have some limitations here.
        Call them "bugs" if you want... :)

        1. Source and destination PAR anims (Input and Output anims)
           @{b}MUST@{ub} be in the same PAR directory !!!

        2. input and/or Output anims names must @{b}NOT@{ub} be a numbers.


           @{b}valid@{ub} names are :

                anim001
                1stanim
                animation
                coolvideo1
                pornoanim

                        etc..


           @{b}NOT@{ub} valid names are:

                1
                001
                123

                        etc...

          You'll get a very weird results if you'll name the Output anim
                with non-valid name.




        3. There's no way to stop this mad programm after you pressed
           the "PROCESS" button !!!
           It will continue until the work will finish !
           If you are full of desire to ens the programm , you can
           exit ADPro. Next time my programm will try to speak to ADPro, it
           will get an error, and exit immediately.




@endnode





