                  Nothing more because I have no free slots more :-(

Software:         PAR programm version 1.89  (not 2.0 )
                  ADPro 2.51 ( diffrence from 2.50 is only 10 bytes
                              changed  :) )
                  Kickstart 3.1 , ver 40.68 , loaded using maprom.
                  Amiga OS3.1, ver. 40.35
                  AS225R2
                  Upd, Arq, KCommodity etc..
                  ImageMasterR/T, ImageFX
                  Real3D2.47, Imahgine3.0,Lightwave3.1+Lightrawe

        All this programs works OK with PARpro...



        Please tell me about your system configuration!




@endnode






@node FUTURE "PARpro Help: Future"



        FUTURE.


        FUTURE IS GREAT, And when you are reading this hypertext, Im working in
