        @{b}First@{ub} that I will do is to implement the configurable, user-definable
        ADPro operator list. So, youll be able to create and insert your own
        ADPro operators in PARpro "process" list.

        @{b}Second@{ub} task is to rewrite it for C or Pascal.

        @{b}Later@{ub} tasks is to implement the following things:
        - Image compositing, Alpha and Color-keyed.
        - Field processing.

*************

